{
  "stem": "13251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, all these years, 50 years, I didn't know that this guy was responsible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't know what to say to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it's-- I mean, I realized it was true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean-- and then later on when we talked, I still couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I asked him, I said-- he was 80 years old at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, how could you, at the age of 29, 30-- What he did was he used to raise money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, first he would recruit these young girls and guys and-- and train them how to approach families so they would release their children, you know, to England or whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they would raise money, because-- because we had to be bought out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It cost money for-- for the-- the Germans to let us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't Jewish, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nicholas Winton.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in fact, as I said, I was very hesitant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't believe this in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I saw my name there-- I mean, where do you find a name like Pinkasovic?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, later on they showed me on the wall there where they had some on exit-- on-- they had--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exhibition of different pictures and stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a full-page article in the local paper about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I just listened to the-- to the video we have from that meeting, and he is mentioned in one of the speakers as one of the people who had-- was-- who made significant effort, and he resulted in-- in saving hundreds of kids.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From mostly Czechoslovakia and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, he himself used to travel back and forth, until the war got real close.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess he'd-- he just sent others.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
